data.description: OHIO CITY/GORDON SQUARE Location, Location, Location! Come check out this lovely duplex located in the middle of a highly desired neighborhood. Remodeled homes and new construction projects abound every which way you look! Local favorites like Forest City Shuffleboard, Herb n Twine, Cleveland Bagel, and Mason's Creamery are just moments away for you to enjoy. Tall ceilings(9' plus) in the lower level are a real plus. Generous city backyard allows for all of your favorite outdoor activities. This home has a lot to offer and would be PERFECT to live out of one half and rent the other to cover a significant portion of your mortgage payment.  (Home is vacant)
